targets.expr:
label_replace(
    histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_client_requests_seconds_bucket{app=~"${component:text}(-(v[0-9]+|canary))?$",}[$__rate_interval])) by (le, http_url, http_method, method, uri, client_name, version)),
    "version", "$1", "app", "${component:text}-(v[0-9]+|canary)|${component:text}$"
  )

label_replace(
    histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket{app=~"${component:text}(-(v[0-9]+|canary))?$", server_address!~"consul.*", server_address!~"vault.*", server_address!~"otel-collector.*", server_address!~"monitoring-metrics.*", server_address!~"shared-metrics-db.*"}[$__rate_interval])) by (le, http_request_method, server_address)),
    "version", "$1", "app", "${component:text}-(v[0-9]+|canary)|${component:text}$"
  )

label_replace(
    histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_okHttpClient_requests_seconds_bucket{app=~"${component:text}(-(v[0-9]+|canary))?$", host!~"consul.*", host!~"vault.*", host!~"otel-collector.*", host!~"monitoring-metrics.*", host!~"shared-metrics-db.*"}[$__rate_interval])) by (le, method, host)),
    "version", "$1", "app", "${component:text}-(v[0-9]+|canary)|${component:text}$"
  )

list.definition:
SELECT id
FROM componentes
WHERE nome = '${component:text}'
list.name: component_id
list.query:
SELECT id
FROM componentes
WHERE nome = '${component:text}'

list.definition:
SELECT CASE WHEN ambiente = 'CAS' THEN '$nome_prometheus_cas'
	   ELSE '$nome_prometheus_aws' END
FROM componentes c
WHERE c.id = $component_id
list.name: nome_prometheus
list.query:
SELECT CASE WHEN ambiente = 'CAS' THEN '$nome_prometheus_cas'
	   ELSE '$nome_prometheus_aws' END
FROM componentes c
WHERE c.id = $component_id

list.definition:
SELECT CASE WHEN mc.tem_auto_instrumentacao IS TRUE THEN '$url_pods_infra_auto' WHEN c.ambiente = 'CAS' THEN '$urls_pods_infra_cas' ELSE '$urls_pods_infra_aws' END
FROM componentes c
JOIN metricas_componente mc ON mc.componente_id = c.id
WHERE c.id = $component_id

WHERE c.id = $component_id
